---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Leadership — Global Faith Temple"
  description="The organization, team, and partner communities — across Vietnam and the allied nations — who steward Global Faith Temple together."
>
  <main>
    <header class="relative bg-ivory pb-16 pt-40 md:pb-24 md:pt-48">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
        <p class="fade-up mb-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-olive opacity-80">Leadership</p>
        <h1 class="fade-up font-serif text-4xl leading-[1.1] text-olive-deep md:text-6xl">
          Stewards, not owners.
        </h1>
        <p class="fade-up mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.78);">
          The temple was given by one man's lifetime of labor. It is now held in trust by a small circle of stewards,
          supported by a wider team of volunteers and the partner communities across Vietnam and the allied nations who
          share in this work.
        </p>
        <div class="fade-up mt-12 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-olive opacity-50">
          <span class="h-px w-10" style="background: rgba(74,76,33,0.4);"></span>
          <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10"><circle cx="5" cy="5" r="1.4" fill="currentColor"></circle></svg>
          <span class="h-px w-10" style="background: rgba(74,76,33,0.4);"></span>
        </div>
        <nav class="fade-up mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-olive opacity-70">
          <a href="#organization" class="hover:text-olive">Organization</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#team" class="hover:text-olive">Team</a><span class="opacity-30">·</span>
          <a href="#communities" class="hover:text-olive">Communities</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Organization -->
    <section id="organization" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Organization</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl text-pretty">A simple structure, held lightly.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-relaxed md:col-span-8" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.82);">
          <p>
            Global Faith Temple is governed by a Council of Stewards — a small group accountable to our community of
            veterans and families, to our partners abroad, and to the founding charter our founder set down with his
            own hand.
          </p>
          <p>
            The day-to-day work is carried by program leads and a wider circle of volunteers. Decisions of any weight
            are made together, in long and patient conversation, rather than by command.
          </p>
          <div class="stagger mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.2);">
              <p class="font-serif text-base text-olive-deep">Council of Stewards</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Sets direction; tends the founding charter; safeguards the temple's purpose.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.2);">
              <p class="font-serif text-base text-olive-deep">Program Leads</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Carry out remembrance, community life, and outreach to veterans and their families.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-t pt-4" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.2);">
              <p class="font-serif text-base text-olive-deep">Volunteer Circle</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">The steady hands behind every meal, every ceremony, every open afternoon.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team -->
    <section id="team" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1); background-color: var(--parchment);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Team</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">The people you may meet here.</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">A small team, drawn from many countries, bound by one purpose.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right md:col-span-8">
          <div class="stagger grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Doug H. Nguyen, PhD</p>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-olive opacity-70">Senior Steward</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Guides daily worship, leads the morning candle ceremony, and offers pastoral care to veterans and families.</p>
              <a href="/leadership/doug-h-nguyen" class="mt-3 inline-block text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-olive transition-colors hover:text-olive-deep">His story →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Jane Smith</p>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-olive opacity-70">Director of Community</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Tends our outreach, gatherings, and the shared meals that knit our visitors into a wider family.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Robert Johnson</p>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-olive opacity-70">Remembrance Coordinator</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Keeps faith with the names — maintaining records, ceremonies, and ties to veterans of the United States and allied nations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fade-up border-l pl-5" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.3);">
              <p class="font-serif text-lg text-olive-deep">Michael Brown</p>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-olive opacity-70">Operations</p>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">Keeps the small lights burning — the building, the records, the quiet logistics of an open temple.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Communities -->
    <section id="communities" class="scroll-mt-24 border-t py-20 md:py-28" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.1);">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-12 px-6 md:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="reveal-left md:col-span-4">
          <p class="mb-4 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-olive opacity-70">Communities</p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight text-olive-deep md:text-4xl">Friends we are honored to walk with.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right space-y-12 md:col-span-8">
          <div id="vietnam" class="fade-up scroll-mt-24 border-l-2 pl-6" style="border-color: rgba(216,168,91,0.6);">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-olive opacity-70">Vietnam</p>
            <p class="mt-3 font-serif text-2xl text-olive-deep">Standing with the families left behind in Vietnam.</p>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.82);">
              We do not run sister sanctuaries abroad. What we do — quietly, year after year — is walk with the widows,
              the children, and the aging comrades of the Republic of Vietnam's soldiers who never came home. A modest
              stipend, a parcel of rice, a letter at the New Year, a hand to hold in their last illness. Our work in
              Vietnam is one of friendship, careful listening, and the simple promise that those who were left behind
              will not be forgotten.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div id="allies" class="fade-up scroll-mt-24 border-l-2 pl-6" style="border-color: rgba(216,168,91,0.6);">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-olive opacity-70">Allied nations</p>
            <p class="mt-3 font-serif text-2xl text-olive-deep">Honoring those who came from afar.</p>
            <p class="mt-3" style="color: rgba(43,42,29,0.82);">
              Beside the soldiers of Vietnam stood six nations who sent their sons and daughters into a war not their
              own. We are bound, in gratitude, to the veterans' communities of each — and we keep their names alongside
              our own.
            </p>
            <ul class="stagger mt-6 grid gap-2 text-sm sm:grid-cols-2" style="color: var(--muted-foreground);">
              <li class="fade-up border-t pt-2" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">— The United States of America</li>
              <li class="fade-up border-t pt-2" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">— The Republic of Korea</li>
              <li class="fade-up border-t pt-2" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">— Australia</li>
              <li class="fade-up border-t pt-2" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">— New Zealand</li>
              <li class="fade-up border-t pt-2" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">— The Kingdom of Thailand</li>
              <li class="fade-up border-t pt-2" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">— The Republic of the Philippines</li>
              <li class="fade-up border-t pt-2" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">— The Republic of China</li>
              <li class="fade-up border-t pt-2" style="border-color: rgba(74,76,33,0.15);">— And the families and elders of each</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
